---
title: Sweet-Soy Chicken & Root Veggies with Creamy Celery Slaw
description: Sometimes it’s too hard to wait for something sweet, so we’ve come up with a plan. Satisfy those cravings with a sweet-soy seaoning on perfectly seared chicken. A creamy slaw will help to elevate things, not to mention the roasted veggies. Enjoy pleasing your tastebuds!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
